<h2>Did You Know?</h2>


<div class="txt-block">
<h4>Trivia</h4>
Features <a  href="/name/nm0384060/">Bernard Hill</a> in a small role. Hill would go on to appear in a Best Picture Oscar winner for each of the following decades: 
<a  href="/title/tt0120338/">Titanic</a> and 
<a  href="/title/tt0167260/">Sagan om konungens &#xE5;terkomst</a>.
<span class="see-more inline"><a class="nobr" href="trivia">See more</a></span>&nbsp;&raquo;

</div>

<hr />
<div class="txt-block">
<h4>Goofs</h4>
Revealing mistakes: 
In the massacre scene Gen. Dyer is pacing back and forth between the two rows of firing soldiers. Right before the cut to the crowd he steps in front of a standing soldier firing.
<span class="see-more inline"><a class="nobr" href="goofs">See more</a></span>&nbsp;&raquo;

</div>

<hr />
<div class="txt-block">
<h4>Quotes</h4>
